text: Ninad Rathva (born 10 March 1999) is an Indian cricketer. He made his first- class debut for Baroda cricket team in the 2017–18 Ranji Trophy on 17 November 2017, where he scored a century in the first innings. He made his Twenty20 debut for Baroda in the 2017–18 Syed Mushtaq Ali Trophy on 21 January 2018. He made his List A debut for Baroda in the 2017–18 Vijay Hazare Trophy on 14 February 2018. ==References== Category:Indian cricketers Category:1999 births Category:Living people
